_azure_get_storage_account_key: [minor] simplify control flow

The loop doesn't break, so the else clause will always execute. I
tripped over this a little while reading it, so thought I'd make the
small change.

bf.copy: fix cloud copy in GCS

It looks like most calls return in a single RPC, but e.g. copying across
different storage classes was probably broken.
more comments, keep metadata when clearing uncommitted blocks
clear uncommitted blocks when writing a file
don't delete blob on write if it's already a block blob
